Package org.cougaar.core.component

Interface Summary
Binder A Binder is an implementation of a BindingSite: that is an implementation of the Service-like relationship API between a child component and its parent.
BinderFactory A BinderFactory provides Binder instances on behalf of a ContainingComponent or ServiceProvider to wrap Child components.
BinderFactoryWrapper An idea for the future: A BinderFactory which encapsulates all BinderFactories known to a component of a lower priority.
BindingSite A BindingSite class names and specifies a specific parent Component (Container) to child Component relationship API, e.g. the API of a parent which a child may invoke.
Component A Component is the base class of the Component and Service Model.
ComponentView A ViewService view of a component, providing visibility into the component's ComponentDescription and advertised/obtained services.
ContainedService A service which may be made available to a contained component which allows access to various controls and information about the context in which the component is loaded.
Container A Component which contains other components.
ContainerAPI ContainerAPI is the interface used by Binder and/or BinderFactory to invoke Binder-privileged methods on the parent Container.
ContainerBinder Binder for a child that is a Container.
ContainerView A ViewService view of a container component, which extends ComponentView by adding child views.
ExtendedServiceBroker A ServiceBroker with extended methods to support the ViewService.
NullService This is a marker API for blocked services.
Service A Service is an abstract Service API which may be supplied by a ServiceProvider which may be registered in a ServiceBroker object.
ServiceAvailableListener Like BeanContextServicesListener
ServiceBroker Cougaar component Service Broker.
ServiceListener Base interface for all service listeners.
ServiceProvider Like BeanContextServiceProvider
ServiceRevokedListener Like BeanContextServiceRevokedListener
ServiceView A ViewService view of an advertised or obtained service.
StateObject An Object that contains internal state.
SubscriptionLifeCycle Hook to start subscriptions as a pseudo life-cycle event
ViewService This service allows a component to see its ComponentDescription, the services it has obtained, and additional component model information.
 

Class Summary
AddonServiceBroker A Simple ServiceBroker which does a simple delegation of service requests for most purposes, except that it has an escape hatch where extending classes may, in effect, themselves offer services directly to the requestors.
BinderBase BinderBase contains logic for the parent link (ContainerAPI) but not the child link.
BinderFactory.BFComparator  
BinderFactorySupport Implement the basics of a BinderFactory.
BinderSupport A Shell implementation of a Binder which does introspection-based initialization and hooks for startup of the child component.
BinderWrapper A base class for a BinderWrapper: A binder which is interposed between a container and another binder.
BindingUtility A collection of utilities to be used for binding components.
ComponentDescription An immutable description of a loadable component (for example, a plugin, servlet, etc).
ComponentDescriptions A utility class for manipulating sets of ComponentDescription objects.
ComponentFactory A base class useful for creating components and instilling the "breath of life" (initial services) on behalf of manager objects.
ComponentFactory.ClassLoaderCache A map of URL to ClassLoader
ComponentModelEvent Service event is a base class for all Service, Binder and Component Model Events, analogous.
ComponentSupport A base class for component implementations.
ContainedBinderSupport A Binder implementation which proxies the ServiceBroker with an AddonServiceBroker offering a ContainedService instance.
ContainerBinderSupport A Shell implementation of a ContainerBinder based upon BinderSupport.
ContainerSupport The standard implementation of a Container.
DelegatingServiceBroker A Simple ServiceBroker which just delegates all queries to another, useful for making restricted extentions.
ExtendedServiceBroker.ServiceResult  
ParameterizedComponent Simple Component base class that provides named paramater support.
PropagatingServiceBroker A service broker which implements not just a local SB, but also a pass-through to another (presumably higher-level) SB.
ServiceAvailableEvent ServiceAvailableEvent indicates that a new service is available to clients of a ServiceBroker.
ServiceBrokerSupport Simple implementation of Cougaar component services layer.
ServiceEvent Service event is a base class for all Service Events
ServiceFilter A BinderFactoryWrapper which wraps components using a Binder which examines and, optionally, modifies, wraps, or audits service requests.
ServiceFilterBinder A Wrapper Binder contructed by ServiceFilter which watches service requests and has convenient overridable points where extensions may monitor, edit, veto or wrap services requested by the client.
ServiceFilterBinder.ServiceTuple  
ServiceRevokedEvent ServiceRevokedEvent indicates that a service has been revoked in a service context.
StateTuple A tuple containing a Component description and the Component's state.
 

Exception Summary
ComponentFactoryException RuntimeException thrown by ComponentFactory This was a checked exception until Cougaar 9.2.
ComponentLoadFailure RuntimeException thrown when a component cannot be loaded.
ComponentRuntimeException Base class ComponentModel RuntimeException.
IncorrectInsertionPointException Marker class for a Container "add(..)" attempt to the wrong component insertion point.
